---
import '../../styles/global.css';
import Integrity from '../../assets/integration.webp';
import Agility from '../../assets/agile.webp';
import Diversity from '../../assets/people.webp';
import Excellence from '../../assets/handshake.webp';
import Commitment from '../../assets/excellence.webp';
---

<section class="mx-auto md:w-8xl text-center py-10 md:py-20 px-4 bg-white text-[#292929]">
  <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-10">
    Empowering Careers. Enabling Companies.
  </h2>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 text-left max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Vision Card -->
    <div class="p-10 bg-[#f5f5f5] leading-relaxed">
      <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold">Our Vision</h3>
      <p class="font-bold my-4">To become the most trusted bridge between talent and opportunity across continents.</p>
      <p>Our vision is to be the most trusted and preferred manpower staffing agency. We are committed to delivering exceptional quality, integrity, and transparency. Our goal is to exceed the expectations of clients and candidates at every step. We build long-term partnerships through tailored staffing solutions. Professionalism and excellence define our approach to every interaction. We empower businesses with top talent and individuals with fulfilling careers.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Mission Card -->
    <div class="p-10 bg-[#e3f1ff] leading-relaxed">
      <h3 class="text-xl md:2xl font-semibold">Our Mission</h3>
      <p class="font-bold my-4">To deliver dynamic staffing solutions through integrity, innovation, and a people-first approach.</p>
      <p>We are on a mission to empower both employers and job seekers through agile, reliable, and future-ready customized recruitment strategies. Every placement is guided by a deep understanding of industry needs and individual aspirations. Powered by advanced technology and a passionate team of experts, we ensure a seamless hiring experience, prioritizing long-term success over short-term gains.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-10 text-center">
  <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold mb-8">Our Core Values</h3>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-5 gap-4 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Value 1 -->
<div class="flex flex-col items-center leading-relaxed">
  <div class="h-28 w-28 bg-[#e3f1ff] rounded-full shadow-md flex items-center justify-center mb-2">
    <img 
      src={Integrity.src} 
      alt="Value 1"
      class="h-16 w-16 object-contain"
    />
  </div>
  <p class="text-lg md:text-xl my-3">Integrity</p>
  <p>We believe in approaching every interaction with transparency and honesty. Trust is the foundation of all our partnerships.</p>
</div>


    <!-- Value 2 -->
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center leading-relaxed">
  <div class="h-28 w-28 bg-[#e3f1ff] rounded-full shadow-md flex items-center justify-center mb-2">
    <img 
      src={Agility.src} 
      alt="Value 1"
      class="h-16 w-16 object-contain"
    />
  </div>
  <p class="text-lg md:text-xl my-3">Agility</p>
  <p>In a rapidly changing job market, we stay ahead by adapting quickly and delivering timely, effective staffing solutions.  </p>
</div>

    <!-- Value 3 -->
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center leading-relaxed">
  <div class="h-28 w-28 bg-[#e3f1ff] rounded-full shadow-md flex items-center justify-center mb-2">
    <img 
      src={Diversity.src} 
      alt="Value 1"
      class="h-16 w-16 object-contain"
    />
  </div>
  <p class="text-lg md:text-xl my-3">Diversity</p>
  <p>We celebrate & champion inclusivity, ensuring equal opportunities for all individuals across backgrounds, cultures, and geographies.</p>
</div>

    <!-- Value 4 -->
   <div class="flex flex-col items-center leading-relaxed">
  <div class="h-28 w-28 bg-[#e3f1ff] rounded-full shadow-md flex items-center justify-center mb-2">
    <img 
      src={Excellence.src} 
      alt="Value 1"
      class="h-16 w-16 object-contain"
    />
  </div>
  <p class="text-lg md:text-xl my-3">Excellence</p>
  <p>We strive for excellence in everything we do, from client service to candidate experience, setting high standards in global recruitment.</p>
</div>

    <!-- Value 5 -->
   <div class="flex flex-col items-center leading-relaxed">
  <div class="h-28 w-28 bg-[#e3f1ff] rounded-full shadow-md flex items-center justify-center mb-2">
    <img 
      src={Commitment.src} 
      alt="Value 1"
      class="h-16 w-16 object-contain"
    />
  </div>
  <p class="text-lg md:text-xl my-3">Commitment</p>
  <p>We are wholeheartedly committed to empowering our clients to achieve lasting success and supporting our candidates every step of the way, from onboarding applications.</p>
</div>
  </div>
</div>
  
</section>
